Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一摔成绩不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 香苗 那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但刚才橘同学抓到你胸部时整个人愣住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝对会兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 指定下一步作战策略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说作战策略?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多 交给我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 快到创立祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如就在营火会上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是创立祭那天茶道部会很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天滑冰真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 纯一你的手套呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近弄不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该赶得上圣诞节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想申请创立祭当天借出备品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那请填写这张申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎样写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下需要用到的备品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子那个挺大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个肉包那么大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 梨穗子的不止这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在那里揉着肉包发呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你叫橘 纯一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么知道我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一个笨蛋却在细节上斤斤计较
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你要跟着来还是不来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 我跟你们走是要做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我们搬一下这东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的山芋片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是帮你们搬被炉的盖板就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真容易说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…你们认识樱井吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我们是第一次见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是茶道部部长 夕月琉璃子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞羽爱歌 是副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来是茶道部的学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这东西这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话的时候把它放下来不就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐垫5张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下给你泡茶 要尝尝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不是懂相关礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝粗茶有什么礼节的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为是茶道部 所以我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不会午休刚过就点沏粉茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也、也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢赞赏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么第一次见面就知道我跟樱井是认识的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 梨穗子一直跟我们说关于你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵起茧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 那家伙说了我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以启齿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多器皿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是茶具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢茶道部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 学姐 我交了创立祭的申请书了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 绚辻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了 看你很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填写茶道部的申请书有点麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一帮我们把这个搬来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是中途介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被炉就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永远在这里这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 安慰奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天帮我们大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如帮人帮到底 在创立祭当天也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 我们这里没男生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们柔弱的女生没办法做重活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你帮忙做体力活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就一言为定 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一在创立祭能过来帮忙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她们人很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定是他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众望所归
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 明天创立祭的准备就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃子学姐泡的茶就是好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉承我也没什么好处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿谀奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这不是客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为无论我怎么努力都泡不了那么好喝的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我们不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗就要给后辈泡茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 也不会有那机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的担心多余了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的创立祭跟去年不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招纳新部员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有梨穗子一个茶道部就会废部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对保护好茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也不用那么起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先跟你商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他收作新部员如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把、把纯一收作部员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之前来活动室的时候也很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过纯一会入部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你们想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞前夜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今年不去创立祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是跟梨穗说好去茶道部帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也跟人约好了 先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在几小时后的集体舞蹈里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要赢得美人归
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你还不死心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的字典里没有放弃二字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至战斗到最后一秒我都绝不松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 用你的眼睛好好看着我的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你立刻帮忙搬运甜米酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部每年都会酿造甜米酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有够重的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后作为答谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会用茶和甜米酒好好款待你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会好好帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你作为茶道部员的意识终于觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是部员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 能帮我放到那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 另外还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入茶道部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 纯一已经来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上这个花了不少时间所以来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨、梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和服很适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一直穿着和服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也很适合两位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后诸葛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来帮忙发传单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小梨穗 你好好教他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边也人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创立祭要做的事情真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我什么都不懂 真的很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏有学姐她们在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今年也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要借此机会加入茶道部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目前还没有那个兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部有甜米酒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在庭院还有茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥有帮上忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他帮我们干了体力活 真是帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美也 我认真做还是能做得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 纱江 我们去茶会好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知还能不能吃到小逢游泳部的关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吃完关东煮再去茶会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:16:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们待会再去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要吃萝卜和…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 别一个劲吃太多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该回茶会那边了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也应该很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在体育馆那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5、4、3、2、1、0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的参赛选手是伊藤香苗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 今天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道谢的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没过这么开心的圣诞节了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加创立祭看来也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过天气真够冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 感觉空气里混有薄荷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸一口气觉得很清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 说得不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过一本小说里是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我有点明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到由梨穗子口中说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得街上那么冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 小时候下雪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子对着天空张大嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部胸部很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了所以在吃雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷冰冰的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃那种东西能填饱肚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 吃得停不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 的确不能填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色圣诞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变冷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能戴上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 手指穿不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得太细了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着带着就会变大的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 很暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没准备什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 生日那天你送我北极熊钥匙扣我都还没回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 梨穗子想要什么就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 想要的东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然这样说 我一时也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用马上说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的战斗永无终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 怎么办呢 香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得要什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗 圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.91,0:23:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给美也的礼物是包暖用内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着凉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样天气再冷 身体也暖烘烘的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊暖烘烘的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻 暖烘烘的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 继承
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美也就送你这肉包当做礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我正在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

